---
import ProjectLayout from "../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
---

<ProjectLayout title="VibeTrip - AI Travel Planning Platform">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">VibeTrip</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
    AI-powered travel planning platform that creates personalized itineraries
    based on user preferences
  </p>

  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      VibeTrip is an innovative AI travel planning platform that leverages
      machine learning to create personalized travel experiences. The platform
      analyzes user preferences, travel history, and real-time data to generate
      custom itineraries that match individual travel styles and interests.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>AI-powered itinerary generation</li>
      <li>Personalized recommendations based on user preferences</li>
      <li>Real-time integration with travel APIs</li>
      <li>Interactive map visualization</li>
      <li>Social sharing and collaboration features</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Frontend: React, Next.js, TypeScript</li>
      <li>Backend: Python, FastAPI</li>
      <li>AI/ML: OpenAI GPT, Custom recommendation algorithms</li>
      <li>Database: PostgreSQL</li>
      <li>Deployment: Vercel, Railway</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Impact</h2>
    <p>
      VibeTrip demonstrates the practical application of AI in the travel
      industry, showcasing how machine learning can enhance user experience and
      provide valuable, personalized services. The project highlights skills in
      full-stack development, AI integration, and product development.
    </p>
  </div>
</ProjectLayout>
